1. *Uhapsili* su dvojicu osumnjičenih za pljačku. (They *arrested* two suspects for robbery.)
2. Kada su *uhapsili* osumnjičenog, pronašli su dokaze koji su potvrdili njegovu krivicu. (When they *arrested* the suspect, they found evidence that confirmed his guilt.)
3. Oni će *uhapsiti* sve osobe koje se budu nalazile na mestu događaja. (They will *arrest* all persons found at the scene.)
4. *Uhapšen* je vozač koji je prouzrokovao nesreću. (The driver who caused the accident was *arrested*.)
5. Policija je sinoć *uhapsila* više osoba zbog posedovanja droge. (Last night, the police *arrested* several individuals for drug possession.)
6. Advokat je zatražio da se njegov klijent *uhapsi* i ispita pre suđenja. (The lawyer requested that his client be *arrested* and interrogated before trial.)
7. Molim vas da me *ne uhapsite*, nisam učinio ništa loše. (Please don't *arrest* me, I haven't done anything wrong.)